metadata.name: Panda Jewel #1
metadata.description:
PANDA JEWELS is a 3D Animated Digital Art collection of up to 2222 NFTs. Panda Jewels are beautiful and complex pieces of art created by the spanish award-winning visual artist Alvaro Martín Treviño. The collection breathes an ecological concept, we consider endangered animals the authentic jewels of this world, this collection is a tribute to them. Each Panda Jewel allows its owner to entry to the Pandaverse, a multiplayer-futuristic colorful jungle with glittery environment like the Panda Jewels.

We want to build a new world full of “Love”, “Light” and “Peace”.

Welcome to the Pandaverse.
